####
npm init => command se hum apni package.json file  bna skte han jiss me hum apne app 
ke sari details enter kar skte han like app name , description , author name , etc .
####

####
package.json me jo commands hum scripts ke andar khud se bnate han un ko chlane ke lye npm run 'command name' use karte han.
and jo special keywords hte han node js ke andar like "start" un ke lye hume "run" keyword ke zarorat nahi parti.

so , inshort jo commands npm "command-name" se na chale but npm run "command-name" se chal jae wo custom commands hte han.
####

####
npm install <dependenciesname> --save-dev mean ke package just uss project ke lye install kiya gya han and ye package only development par chle ga . production par nahi.

agr hum global keyword ke sath dependency install kare ge to wo hmare globally machine par install ho jae ge.
####
